response.overview: Sometimes white men get tired of the white meat. That's when they go searching for chocolate. It doesn't matter if it's creamy brown or a rich deep dark chocolate, as long as she tastes sweet and fucks real well. Yasmine De Leon gets more than her computer fixed. Ana Foxxx makes a white man's dream come true. Aryana Adin wants to surprise her hubby with some sexy pictures from a professional photographer, she gets more than pictures. Jordan Skye needs a plumber for more than just her clogged sink in the kitchen.
response.title: White Men Lovin' Chocolate
